    "present a differential framework example for freestyle material capturing (Ma et al. 2021).",
    "This technique improves sampling efficiency and enhances the precision of material properties, which in turn enables the creation of more realistic virtual objects in the Metaverse.",
    "Additionally, modelling and rendering can be carried out with the help of a variety of software tools, which can be divided into three categories.",
    "First off, engineers and designers can make models by entering real-world data, such the materials and weight, using parametric 3D modelling or CAD (Computer Aided Design) tools like AutoCAD and SketchUp.",
    "Additionally, polygon models made using 3D Max, Maya, or Blender are more concept-focused than measurement-focused."
